videos.headline: Western Kentucky flea-flicker for a gain of 59
videos.description: Mike White pass complete to Taywan Taylor for 59 yds Taywan Taylor fumbled, recovered by WKent Taywan Taylor for a 1ST down

videos.headline: Hurts' 63-yard pass to Stewart falls just short of end zone
videos.description: Alabama QB Jalen Hurts throws a deep 63-yard pass to ArDarius Stewart, who gets tackled just short of the end zone.

videos.headline: Alabama creates first turnover of the day
videos.description: Nacarius Fant pass intercepted Ronnie Harrison return for a loss of 6 yards to the WKent 33

videos.headline: Hurts finds Ridley for score
videos.description: Alabama QB Jalen Hurts throws a short pass to Calvin Ridley in the flat for a four-yard touchdown reception.

videos.headline: Alabama DB Jackson extends lead with pick-six
videos.description: Alabama DB Eddie Jackson intercepts a pass and returns the ball 55 yards for the touchdown to extend the Crimson Tide's lead over Western Kentucky.

videos.headline: B. Barnett pass,to A. Stewart for 52 yds for a 1ST down

videos.headline: Scarbrough scampers in for 2-yard TD run
videos.description: Alabama running back Bo Scarbrough runs in for a 2-yard touchdown to increase the Crimson Tide's lead to 31-3 over Western Kentucky.

videos.headline: B. Emmons gets in for 6 yard TD run

videos.headline: Western Kentucky first TD of the game

videos.headline: Alabama LB penalized for slamming Western Kentucky QB to ground
videos.description: Alabama LB Tim Williams body slams Western Kentucky QB Mike White to the ground after White got rid of the ball, resulting in a penalty.

videos.headline: Tide rolls over Western Kentucky
videos.description: Alabama quarterback Jalen Hurts throws two touchdown passes as the top ranked Crimson Tide defeat the Hilltoppers 38-10.
